text: Michał Bartczak (born 27 February 1987) is a Polish handball player for the Polish national team. He is currently a free agent.EHF profile He participated at the 2013 World Men's Handball Championship. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:People from Pabianice Category:Polish male handball players Category:Vive Kielce players
